profile:
Lethbridge Elite Roofing has provided quality roofing and renovation services in Southern Alberta for over a decade.
 
Our dedicated expert technicians offer superior installations and with award winning, designer roofing systems such as Euro-Shield and DaVinci products. Our repair and maintenance service team consists of red-seal roofing technicians and carefully screened trained laborers. We care for our team members as much as we care about our customers; thus our teams are supervised by an accredited National Construction Safety Officer certified by the Alberta Construction Safety Association. provided with top of the line roof products.
 
We believe in providing expert advice, friendly service and best value every time
Thank you for choosing Lethbridge Elite Roofing as your partner in your home improvement!
